Frontend Redesign Implementation Plan                                                                                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ Context                                                                                                                                                                                    │
│                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ Barry (designer) has delivered HTML/CSS templates in nn-templates/ (cloned from github.com/barrycosta/nn-templates). These templates define the complete design system: colors, fonts,     │
│ breakpoints, accessible navigation, overlay system, header, footer, and page structure. The existing PLAN Google Sheet has 112 tasks but none cover integrating Barry's design system.     │
│ Robert's 40 existing tasks are all bug fixes and feature work on the current codebase (tasks 5-8, 52-78, 103-110).                                                                         │
│                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ This plan adds new tasks for the design system integration. It does NOT duplicate existing tasks.                                                                                          │
│                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ Execution Plan                                                                                                                                                                             │
│                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ Use scripts/google_sheets/sheets_client.py to append all 20 tasks (113-132) to the PLAN sheet. Each task will be appended as a row with the columns: Task #, Ticket, Category, Task Title, │
│  Description, Assigned To, Priority, Status, Start Date, Due Date, Week, Dependencies, Notes.                                                                                              │
│                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ Steps:                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ 1. Run python -m scripts.google_sheets.sheets_client next-task to confirm the next task number is 113                                                                                      │
│ 2. Append each task row using the append CLI command                                                                                                                                       │
│ 3. Verify with python -m scripts.google_sheets.sheets_client count plan that 20 new rows were added                                                                                        │
│                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ ---                                                                                                                                                                                        │
│ Existing Tasks Overlap Check                                                                                                                                                               │
│                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ No duplicates found. The 112 existing tasks cover:                                                                                                                                         │
│ - Tasks 1-4: Critical backend blockers (Manav)                                                                                                                                             │
│ - Tasks 5-8: Critical frontend bug fixes (Robert) - copy address, share dropdown, hours toggle, verified badge                                                                             │
│ - Tasks 9-51: Admin backend features (Manav)                                                                                                                                               │
│ - Tasks 52-53: SEO components (Robert)                                                                                                                                                     │
│ - Tasks 54-61: Nearby feature fixes (Robert)                                                                                                                                               │
│ - Tasks 62-69: Frontend detail page fixes (Robert)                                                                                                                                         │
│ - Tasks 70-72: Map fixes (Robert)                                                                                                                                                          │
│ - Tasks 73-78: Infrastructure/SEO/Blog (mixed)                                                                                                                                             │
