│ Task 116 - Create Accessibility Foundation (AAA Compliance)                                                                                                                                │
│                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ Category: Frontend Accessibility                                                                                                                                                           │
│ Assigned To: Robert (Barry provides code/guidance)                                                                                                                                         │
│ Priority: P0 - Critical                                                                                                                                                                    │
│ Dependencies: 113                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ Description:                                                                                                                                                                               │
│ Set up the accessibility infrastructure that every component needs. AAA compliance is mandatory from day one per the meeting.                                                              │
│                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ Must implement:                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ 1. Skip-main link: <a class="skip-main" href="#main_content">Skip to main content</a> - hidden until focused, then visible                                                                 │
│ 2. Focus-visible styles: :focus-visible { outline: 3px solid #0066cc; outline-offset: 2px; } - only shows for keyboard, not mouse clicks                                                   │
│ 3. Visually hidden class: .visually_hidden - hides text visually but keeps for screen readers (for labels, hints)                                                                          │
│ 4. Reduced motion: @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) - disable animations                                                                                                            │
│ 5. High contrast: @media (prefers-contrast: high) - ensure borders and outlines visible                                                                                                    │
│ 6. 44px minimum touch targets: All buttons/links on mobile must be at least 44x44px                                                                                                        │
│ 7. Color contrast: All text/background combos must pass AAA (7:1 ratio for normal text, 4.5:1 for large text). Barry's color sheet in Figma already maps which color combos are AAA-safe.  │
│                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ Files to create: nearby-app/app/src/styles/accessibility.css                                                                                                                               │
│ Files to modify: nearby-app/app/src/App.jsx (add skip-main link, id="main_content" on <main>)                                                                                              │
│                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ ---                                                                                                                                                                                        │
│ Phase 2: Shell Components (Week 2)                                                                                                                                                         │
