│                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ Category: Frontend Components                                                                                                                                                              │
│ Assigned To: Robert (Manav assists with React patterns)                                                                                                                                    │
│ Priority: P0 - Critical                                                                                                                                                                    │
│ Dependencies: 113, 116                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ Description:                                                                                                                                                                               │
│ Convert Barry's vanilla JS overlay system (nn-templates/inc/overlay.js) into a reusable React component + hook. This system is used for both the search overlay and the mobile nav         │
│ overlay.                                                                                                                                                                                   │
│                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ Features to port:                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ - Open/close with toggle behavior                                                                                                                                                          │
│ - Backdrop click to close                                                                                                                                                                  │
│ - Escape key to close                                                                                                                                                                      │
│ - Focus trap (Tab cycles through interactive elements inside overlay only)                                                                                                                 │
│ - Body scroll lock (overflow: hidden on body when open)                                                                                                                                    │
│ - Chevron scroll indicator (appears when content overflows, fades on scroll)                                                                                                               │
│ - Focus restoration (returns focus to trigger button when closing)                                                                                                                         │
│ - Auto-focus management (focus on specified element or close button when opening)                                                                                                          │
│ - Skip nav overlay open at desktop (1200px+) for nav overlay specifically                                                                                                                  │
│                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ React implementation:                                                                                                                                                                      │
│ - useOverlay(id) hook - returns { isOpen, open, close, toggle, overlayRef }                                                                                                                │
│ - <Overlay> component - renders backdrop + panel + close button + chevron                                                                                                                  │
│ - CSS from nn-templates/inc/overlay.scss ported to plain CSS                                                                                                                               │
│                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ Files to create: nearby-app/app/src/hooks/useOverlay.js, nearby-app/app/src/components/Overlay.jsx, nearby-app/app/src/components/Overlay.css                                              │
│ Source: nn-templates/inc/overlay.js (206 lines), nn-templates/inc/overlay.scss (442 lines)                                                                                                 │
