│ After implementation, test by:                                                                                                                                                             │
│ 1. Run locally: cd nearby-app && docker compose -f docker-compose.dev.yml up --build                                                                                                       │
│ 2. Frontend: http://localhost:8003 (dev with hot reload)                                                                                                                                   │
│ 3. Backend API: http://localhost:8002                                                                                                                                                      │
│ 4. Test mobile nav at < 1200px width (Chrome DevTools responsive mode)                                                                                                                     │
│ 5. Test desktop nav at > 1200px width                                                                                                                                                      │
│ 6. Test search overlay opens from both mobile bottom bar and desktop header                                                                                                                │
│ 7. Test keyboard navigation: Tab through entire site                                                                                                                                       │
│ 8. Run Lighthouse accessibility audit (target: 95+ score)                                                                                                                                  │
│ 9. Verify all colors match Barry's Accessible Colors Figma spec           